1
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,600
I was from a good family.

2
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:19,200
Because of his greed and his evil,

3
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,440
my family was ruined.

4
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,520
I was reduced to a demon for a hundred years.

5
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,280
How can I let it go?

6
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,800
To you,

7
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:32,600
did your husband really only leave you with hatred?

8
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,200
So what if there was?

9
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:39,200
What he did to me

10
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,890
cannot be made up for by any affection.

11
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:44,440
You only know the grudges in your heart,

12
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,800
but you don't understand the cause and effect.

13
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,600
Do you know

14
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:50,520
that you, your husband, and the maid

15
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:53,490
have been entangled for three lifetimes?

16
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:56,970
This ill-fated relationship could have ended in this life.

17
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,920
In the next life, you could have lived in peace

18
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:02,200
and spent a peaceful life.

19
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:04,360
But because of your hatred and delusion,

20
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,020
you fell into the demonic path

21
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,640
and cannot enter reincarnation.

22
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:09,640
And killed so many innocent people.

23
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,440
With your behavior,

24
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,890
the world will not forgive you.

25
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:14,850
The Way of Heaven

26
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:17,100
won't forgive you either.

27
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:21,360
Three lifetimes of ill-fated romance.

28
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,600
So what?

29
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:26,000
I don't care about past or future lives.

30
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:28,840
I only want satisfaction in this life.

31
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,500
Your sins are too deep,

32
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:32,620
and your obsession is too strong.

33
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:34,560
If you are unwilling to save yourself,

34
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,880
today I

35
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,140
will personally save you.

36
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,120
Sanshan Liujin Immortal,

37
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,720
we have been looking for you for a long time.

38
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,920
Seeing you today,

39
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:46,040
you are indeed extraordinary.

40
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,240
I may not be able to defeat you.

41
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,120
But my benefactor, Lady Tu,

42
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,000
might just be your match.

43
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,240
The Tu clan again.

44
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,840
You're also one of the Four Demons of the Tu Sect.

45
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,960
Ignorant child.

46
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:59,720
How do you know about the Four Demons of the Tu Sect?

47
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:02,780
Thunder Dragon has already been subdued by the master.

48
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,600
Don't be smug.

49
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:10,560
Among the Four Demons, Thunder Dragon and I have the weakest powers.

50
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:14,280
When we regroup and attack again,

51
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,570
we will make everyone in Er City

52
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,160
die with you.

53
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:23,040
We will meet again.

54
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:47,000
Who are you?

55
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:03,320
Lady Tu will avenge me.

56
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,770
It seems to be a misunderstanding.

57
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,700
The Golden Immortal of the Three Mountains.

58
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,500
Her Ladyship has found the Golden Immortal.

59
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,720
He killed Ruixi.

60
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,520
The town where Ruixi was located

61
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:34,260
is only a few dozen miles away from the Thunder Dragon's place.

62
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:37,840
There has been no news from the Thunder Dragon for several days.

63
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,320
It must be his doing too.

64
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:44,520
The Thunder Dragon and Ruixi are just worn-out shoes.

65
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,600
Helping me find the Golden Immortal

66
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:50,200
can be considered a complete merit.

67
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:54,000
I am willing to capture the Golden Immortal for Her Ladyship.

68
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,640
I am willing to go along.

69
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:05,120
You two have followed me for hundreds of years.

70
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:07,400
Although the Golden Immortal has lost his immortal body,

71
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,800
he is not that easy to deal with.

72
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,240
Don't let me down.

73
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,960
Yes, yes.

74
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,600
Thank you, immortal.

75
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:40,320
I thank you on behalf of the people of Ercheng.

76
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:42,159
No need for formalities, County Deputy.

77
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:42,960
Please get up.

78
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,600
And who are you?

79
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:56,240
Paying respects to my ancestor.

80
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,720
Who is your ancestor?

81
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,600
Hey, who are you?

82
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:11,100
You're so young, why are you claiming relatives randomly?

83
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,400
Forgive my rudeness.

84
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,360
Allow me to introduce myself.

85
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:18,560
I am a third-rank sorcerer of the Sitian Tower,

86
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:20,640
Hu San.

87
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:28,760
He's really an official from the Bureau of Astronomy.

88
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,970
A badge of the Bureau of Astronomy.

89
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,460
Who would dare to forge it?

90
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:36,039
Forgive my impoliteness.

91
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,500
Forgive my impoliteness.

92
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,440
Rise.

93
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:41,480
What does the Bureau of Astronomy do?

94
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,840
They belong to the imperial court.

95
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:47,170
They are like official monster catchers.

96
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,160
You are wrong about that, miss.

97
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,800
The Sitian Bureau observes celestial phenomena,

98
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,200
and establishes the calendar.

99
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,840
Above, we manage the destiny of the dynasty.

100
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,900
Below, we handle worldly disasters.

101
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:03,380
Catching demons is just something we do in passing.

102
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,720
Since Ercheng has been occupied by demons for so many years,

103
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:06,840
why didn't you come earlier?

104
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:08,920
Didn't I just say it?

105
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,760
There are simply too many things in this world

106
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,760
to manage.

107
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:15,120
There are countless demons all over the world.

108
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:17,120
And the people in the Sitian Bureau

109
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:19,400
are all one in a million

110
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,560
elites.

111
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:23,530
We really can't attend to everything.

112
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,800
However, logically speaking,

113
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,840
all these states and realms,

114
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,600
since the Sitian Bureau

115
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:33,600
placed Guanxin Mirrors in the government offices to guard them,

116
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:36,160
should have been protected.

117
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:39,240
I sent a pigeon to the capital for help.

118
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,800
But Ruixi is too capable.

119
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:43,330
She intercepts any message leaving the city.

120
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:50,360
This star mirror had already...

121
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,330
Country.

122
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:07,960
It seems the star mirrors everywhere need repairing.

123
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,120
I was ordered to go to Mount Leiting.

124
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,680
Rumor has it that monsters are causing trouble there.

125
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:15,040
But halfway there,

126
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:16,440
I saw a group of constables.

127
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,440
They told me

128
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:21,120
they ran into a monster at a country inn.

129
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,720
They also gave me a portrait.

130
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:34,440
Let me see it.

131
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,640
I reckon,

132
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:41,840
with your speed,

133
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,960
you should have arrived at Er City by now.

134
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,760
Constables.

135
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,680
Master,

136
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:48,800
it's those corrupt officials who want to rob our gold and silver.

137
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,960
Then what will you do?

138
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:52,640
Capture him?

139
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:55,040
The ancestor is a Golden Immortal descended to the mortal realm.

140
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:57,160
The dispute with the constables must be a misunderstanding.

141
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:59,800
I will report to the Sitian Tower to revoke the bounty,

142
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:02,360
and then apprehend the constables for interrogation.

143
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:03,160
Oh right,

144
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:04,520
the monster on Leiting Mountain

145
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:06,980
has already been eliminated by the two of us.

146
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:12,320
I admire your actions, ancestor.

147
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,480
I told you.

148
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:16,060
I am not your ancestor.

149
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:22,600
I cultivate the Hu family shamanic path.

150
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:24,600
You are the legendary Golden Immortal.

151
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,600
As far as I know,

152
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:28,200
you voluntarily descended to the mortal realm for some unknown reason.

153
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,600
But reincarnated as a Qingqiu demon fox.

154
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:34,440
In terms of seniority and experience,

155
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,240
you are my ancestor.

156
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,320
The Master is a demon?

157
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:40,840
Isn't he an immortal?

158
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,400
What does this mean?

159
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,130
Don't ask if you don't understand.

160
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,560
Who you are

161
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,360
has nothing to do with me.

162
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:53,100
You just said it yourself.

163
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:56,440
That demoness is backed by the great Tu demon.

164
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:58,690
They will surely come for revenge.

165
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:01,240
Since you are from the Sitian Bureau,

166
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:03,570
I'll leave the safety of this place to you.

167
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,200
Farewell.

168
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,440
Wait.

169
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:08,320
If you leave,

170
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,320
how will I report to His Majesty?

171
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,720
Are you trying to stop me?
